Package: flextable
Type: Package
Title: Tabular Reporting API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("David", "Gohel", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "david.gohel@ardata.fr"))
Description: Create pretty tables for 'Microsoft Word', 'Microsoft PowerPoint' and 'HTML' documents. 
  An API is provided to let users create tables, modify and format their content. 
  It extends package 'officer' that does not contain any feature for customised tabular reporting. 
  Function 'tabwid' produces an 'htmlwidget' ready to be used in 'Shiny' or 'rmarkdown' documents.
  See the 'flextable' website for more information.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Depends: officer
Imports:
    utils,grDevices,
    dplyr,lazyeval,purrr,tibble,magrittr,tidyr, 
    htmltools,htmlwidgets,
    gdtools
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Suggests: rmarkdown, knitr,
    xml2, 
    testthat, 
    ionicons
VignetteBuilder: knitr
